data.description: Great 4 bedroopm, 3 car garage home in new Subdivision in the Cypress Lakes/Grays Creek area. Lot is almost 1/2 acre.  Nice front porch entry, Formal Dining Room, very open kitchen w/island, granite counter tops, staggered cabinets, tile backsplash, full S.S. Appliance Package, w/Breakfast Nook overlooking the Large Family Room that features a stone surround gas fireplace w/adjacent 1/2 bath. Covered Back Porch, Upstairs features large Master Bedroom, huge closet, dual vanities in bath w/tile surround garden tub & separate shower, very large closet. 3 other very spacious bedrooms w/ample closet space & dual vanity bathroom w/tub-shower comb. Laundry Room is upstairs, Ceiling Fans in all bedrooms. Laminate flooring on 1st floor, tile in bathrooms, carpet in bedrooms. Country Feel but close to 87, I-95, 301, shopping, eateries, new baseball stadium & golf course.  Cumberland County taxes only, Great Schools.  ONLY 5 HOUSES LEFT IN PHASE 1 - HURRY THIS ONE WON'T LAST.
